help.title: Common Commands [{0}]

commands.ban: List of Banned users or BAN some users
commands.dump: Output to file, users, emojis, channels, messages.
commands.help: List of common commands, or displays help of specified command.
commands.lookup: Show user info. (Bans, Ban reasons, Ban proofs)
commands.mute: Mute/Unmute that user(do not use any roles)
commands.purge:
Remove message.
No args: Attempt all messages on that channel until bot has got rate limiting.
[1-100]: Remove specified number
Other arguments, please see following URL.
commands.resetnick: Reset nickname specified user. (Default: the bot)
commands.setbanrep:
Set auto banning reputation.
Default: 5
If joined user's reputation is less than settings, they will be banned.
commands.banrep:
[Alias of setbanrep]

Set auto banning reputation.
Default: 5
If joined user's reputation is less than settings, they will be banned.
commands.notifyrep:
[Alias of setnotifyrep]

Set notify reputation.
Default: 1
If joined user's reputation is less than settings, they will be notified to server owner.
commands.setignore: You can set exclude channel from logging, but can set only one. (If set once, cannot be removed settings, but can change.)
commands.setlog:
Set logging channel.
Not fully completed this feature.
commands.setnotifyrep:
Set notify reputation.
Default: 1
If joined user's reputation is less than settings, they will be notified to server owner.
commands.setwelcome:
Set joined message.
Please set channel, message, both options.
Also see: [here](https://github.com/BlackListener/BlackListener)
commands.welcome:
[Alias of setwelcome]

Set joined message.
Please set channel, message, both options.
Also see: [here](https://github.com/BlackListener/BlackListener)
commands.status:
Displays Minecraft, Fortnite status.
Please note Fortnite has rate limiting.
commands.token: Send bot token to DM. [Bot owner only]
commands.unban:
Unban specified user.
Reputation will be returned, but can't remove proofs, and reasons.
